Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:39.60,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6\fad(150,150)}&\NA\Nn\Ns\Nw\Ne\Nr
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:44.08,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}聞こえないふりが上手になって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.69,0:01:44.70,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fad(150,150)}Q\Nu\Ne\Ns\Nt\Ni\No\Nn
